 you see the trade of is having a server without No-Drop on anything of value. TLC seems to keep the farmers, and the outright rude people far away from this server.<br><br>I play EQ on Firona Vie in relative peace and ease, hardly any of my camps taken, surrounded by a bunch of good people, and a very nice population which out numbers dewds 10 to 1.<br><br>I for one can not and will not imagine a server where a lvl 60 can sit in the bottom of the dungeon and farm. I cannot imagine working my way to the boss of a dungeon to find a level 60 shouting &quot;camp taken&quot;<br><br>With all these stout rules, Firona Vie attracts a certain personality, <br>#1 ones who desire roleplay<br>#2 people who are not affraid to work for their loot.<br><br>/Roleplay assumes that you care to socialize.<br><br>With the good natured, fine people I am surrounded with on Firona Vie, I never seem to have troubled relaxing for hours at a time, a server where personal conflict, and KS's are the rarity, not the norm.<br><br>TLC, Alignment,language, one charachter tough? Find another server! Leave us with our rules, we are happy with them. Don't want these rules? Don't complain just go to another server.<br><br>/rant off <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udorphen01.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dorphen 01</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/30/02 7:32:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2209.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Trivial loot code. friend or foe?</span><hr size=1> I love the TLC I would gladly trade being able to do lower lvl quests. Just to ensure that we don't have 10 lvl 60 farmers in every low lvl dungeon known to man fighting over scrap's <p><img src=